            "id": 5981856,
            "title": "〈美股13F報告〉索羅斯前軍師Q1增持台積電、出清Alphabet",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>傳奇投資人朱肯米勒 (Stanley Druckenmiller) 旗下全球頂級家族辦公室 Duquesne Family Office 15 日揭露，第一季全面出清對 Google 母公司 Alphabet (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GOOGL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GOOGL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GOOGL-US</a>)的持股，並調整多項重要科技與航空類股部位。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>朱肯米勒曾是金融巨鱷索羅斯 (George Soros) 的軍師，曾在 1992 年替索羅斯量子基金策動放空<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/gbpusd\">英鎊</a>交易，大賺 10 億美元，這場經典戰役也奠定他作為全球最頂尖宏觀避險基金經理之一的地位。</p></section><section>\n</section><div class=\"dzbcd51\"></div><div class=\"m1aaic49\"></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>根據週四向美國證券交易委員會 (SEC) 提交的 13F 報告，Duquesne Family Office 在第一季減碼亞馬遜 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMZN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMZN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMZN-US</a>) 與特斯拉 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSLA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSLA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSLA-US</a>)，同時新建倉 AppLovin (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:APP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/APP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">APP-US</a>)股票，並加碼台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>)。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img alt=\"(圖片：shutterstock)\" data-height=\"506\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.5019762845849802\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5981856/m/b2695ffacb544c53ddb18aa317c36582.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5981856/l/b2695ffacb544c53ddb18aa317c36582.jpg\" srcset=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5981856/l/b2695ffacb544c53ddb18aa317c36582.jpg 1x,https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5981856/xl/b2695ffacb544c53ddb18aa317c36582.jpg 2x,https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5981856/xxl/b2695ffacb544c53ddb18aa317c36582.jpg 3x\"/>\n<figcaption>索羅斯前軍師 Q1 增持台積電、出清 Alphabet (圖片：shutterstock)</figcaption>\n</figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>此外，Duquesne 也縮減對美國航空類股的押注，包括出清與美國航空 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AAL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AAL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AAL-US</a>) 相關的看漲期權部位，以及減碼達美航空 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DAL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DAL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DAL-US</a>) 與聯合航空 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:UAL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/UAL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">UAL-US</a>) 等持股。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國航空股於第一季整體表現乏力，反映在該季的部位調整上。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至第一季末，該基金最大持股為 Natera (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NTRA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NTRA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NTRA-US</a>)，其次為長期投資的 Teva Pharmaceutical (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TEVA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TEVA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TEVA-US</a>)。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>值得注意的是，Duquesne 也增持南韓電商酷澎 (Coupang) (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CPNG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CPNG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CPNG-US</a>)，此股現已躍升為其主要持倉之一。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
